To evaluate which model was best suited to describe these processes, and the error function (Ferror) were analyzed; a lower result from the error function indicated a smaller difference between adsorption capacity calculated by the model (Qcalc) and the experimental (Qexp). Ferror can be expressed according to Eq. (8) [35]:8Ferror=∑i=0P(Qi,calc-Qi,expQi,exp)2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
