				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R_\text{L} = \frac{1}{{(1 - K_\text{L} C_0 )}}$$\end{document}where KL and C0 are the same as defined before. The value of RL calculated from the above expression. The nature of the adsorption process to be either unfavorable (RL > 1), linear (RL = 1), favourable (0 < RL < 1) or irreversible (RL = 0).
